title: Sunday Comics: Jelly
text:
Hello! It’s time for Kotaku’s Sunday Comics, your weekly roundup of the best webcomics.

Awkward Zombie by Katie Tiedrich. Published Sept. 30. Read more of Awkward Zombie.

Clueless Hero by Luis Lee and Ana Gaby Perez. Published Oct. 1. Read more of Clueless Hero.

Double XP by M.S. Corley and Josh Crandall. Published Oct. 2. Read more of Double XP.

Life in Aggro by Fei Hsiao and Cecilia Vasquez. Published Oct. 6. Read more of Life in Aggro.

Nerf NOW!! by Josué Pereira. Published Oct. 5. Read more of Nerf NOW!!

Penny Arcade by Jerry Holkins and Mike Krahulik. Published Oct. 4. Read more of Penny Arcade.
